      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation must be under version control with documented test suite; all simulation scripts archived with checksums. Required level 2 mandates documented QA procedures and traceable software versions.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under institutional software QA protocol. Version control via Git repository with tagged release. Unit test suite executed prior to production runs with all tests passing. Simulation scripts archived in institutional repository with SHA-256 checksums recorded."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code must demonstrate second-order spatial convergence on a manufactured solution for the governing Navier-Stokes equations relevant to the blood pump flow regime.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to steady incompressible Navier-Stokes equations. Observed order of accuracy of 1.97 on structured grids, consistent with second-order finite volume scheme. Benchmark test cases from ASME V&V 20 suite executed with errors within published tolerance bands."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) for hemolysis index QoI must be below 5% on the production mesh, assessed using Richardson extrapolation across three systematically refined grids.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed with refinement ratio r=1.3. GCI for normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) computed as 2.1% on the fine mesh, satisfying the required level 2 threshold. Achieved level 3 reflects that asymptotic range was confirmed and extrapolated value reported."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
